Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.43,0:23:09.98,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}相遇就是SHOCKWAVE！SHOCKWAVE！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.98,0:23:12.81,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}向着未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.81,0:23:14.98,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}開始前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.98,0:23:17.48,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}無謀的挑戰者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.48,0:23:19.90,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}就用手中的刀刃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.98,0:23:22.74,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}去開拓明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.86,0:23:25.06,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}不是任何其他人的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.06,0:23:28.79,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}是只屬於自己的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:35.21,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}{\an8}'Cause we're still ROUGH DIAMONDS on the road!